<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Robertson Athokpam - Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .above-Header {
            display: flex;
        }
        
        header {
            
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%; 
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            z-index: 100;
            transition: top 0.3s; 
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 0; 
            width: 100%;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .background-image {
            background-image: url('https://d1fufvy4xao6k9.cloudfront.net/images/blog/posts/2024/01/screenshot_14.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 600px; 
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 60px; 
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); 
        }

        .profile-pic {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            padding: 10px;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 80%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="above-Header">
        <header id="header">
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>
    </div>
    <section id="home" class="background-image">
        <div class="overlay">
            <img src="https://d1fufvy4xao6k9.cloudfront.net/images/blog/posts/2024/01/screenshot_14.jpg" alt="Robertson Athokpam" class="profile-pic">
            <h1>Robertson Athokpam</h1>
            <p>Sophomore at NIT Manipur, Graduating in 2027</p>
            <p>Country: India, State: Manipur</p>
            <p>Looking for Opportunities</p>
        </div>
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/robertson-athokpam-377497293/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/robertsonathokpam" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://x.com/RobertsonA25659" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
            <p>Phone: +91-9366799608</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hi, I'm Robertson Athokpam, a sophomore at NIT Manipur. I am passionate about technology and always eager to learn new things. I am currently looking for opportunities to grow my skills and contribute to exciting projects.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="portfolio">
        <h2>Portfolio</h2>
        <div class="gallery">
            <div class="portfolio-item">
                <img src="/images/project1.jpg" alt="Project 1">
                <h3>Project Title 1</h3>
                <p>A brief description of Project 1. This project showcases my skills in [relevant technology or domain].</p>
                <a href="https://link-to-project1.com" target="_blank">View Project</a>
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-item">
                <img src="/images/project2.jpg" alt="Project 2">
                <h3>Project Title 2</h3>
                <p>A brief description of Project 2. This project showcases my skills in [relevant technology or domain].</p>
                <a href="https://link-to-project2.com" target="_blank">View Project</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more portfolio items as needed -->
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <form action="/contact" method="POST">
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send</button>
        </form>
    </section>
